- That's the plan.

138
00:09:15,389 --> 00:09:17,099
Even the... even the parts about sherrod?

139
00:09:17,641 --> 00:09:18,809
Yeah.

140
00:09:22,563 --> 00:09:24,523
What good is...
What good is a story like that?

141
00:09:24,606 --> 00:09:25,607
Like what?

142
00:09:26,483 --> 00:09:28,403
Like me, sherrod.
Gettin' high. Not gettin' high.

143
00:09:28,485 --> 00:09:29,845
My sister, all that shit in there.

144
00:09:30,154 --> 00:09:32,314
What good do any of that
do to put it in the newspaper?

145
00:09:32,406 --> 00:09:35,451
People read it, they think about it.
Maybe see things different.

146
00:09:36,285 --> 00:09:37,453
I don't know, man.

147
00:09:37,828 --> 00:09:39,788
Bubs, you don't want me
to do this, I won't do it.

148
00:09:43,584 --> 00:09:44,626
I don't know.

149
00:09:46,003 --> 00:09:49,381
Baltimore sun. A little
bit of sun. Sun paper.

150
00:09:49,757 --> 00:09:51,693
Look, Rupert, go public
with this thing if you want

151
00:09:51,717 --> 00:09:55,113
but your shop is gonna come out looking worse
for letting it happen in the first place.

152
00:09:55,137 --> 00:09:57,347
