Can I have a word
with you in private, bill?

161
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:31,215
Hey, if rawls isn't in, I'm not either.

162
00:10:31,381 --> 00:10:33,759
Oh, I wouldn't worry
about bill rawls.

163
00:10:33,842 --> 00:10:38,096
I believe he's about to have
one of those road to Damascus moments.

164
00:10:40,432 --> 00:10:42,059
I can see what you're thinking in there.

165
00:10:42,142 --> 00:10:45,354
I can see the gears grinding
in that head of yours.

166
00:10:48,649 --> 00:10:51,485
You're thinking, "hey, I might have
some wood on carcetti here.

167
00:10:52,236 --> 00:10:54,655
"There's no way they can
pin the blame on me for this fiasco

168
00:10:54,738 --> 00:10:56,907
