in exchange for you shutting the fuck up

175
00:11:13,006 --> 00:11:14,341
and doing what you're told.

176
00:11:15,217 --> 00:11:17,010
And you know what,
bill? You're not far off.

177
00:11:17,094 --> 00:11:19,930
You do have a little leverage
here but just a little.

178
00:11:20,556 --> 00:11:22,099
I wouldn't overplay your hand.

179
00:11:23,308 --> 00:11:24,518
How would you play it?

180
00:11:25,102 --> 00:11:26,687
I'd shut the fuck up and wait your turn

181
00:11:26,770 --> 00:11:29,314
