186
00:11:37,114 --> 00:11:38,782
you're just about right for the msp.

187
00:11:44,204 --> 00:11:46,748
- I have your word?
- And I have yours.

188
00:11:57,301 --> 00:11:58,802
Back channel is the way to go.

189
00:11:59,428 --> 00:12:03,223
See? The police commissioner
done fell off his ass.

190
