229
00:14:40,881 --> 00:14:42,316
You're gonna buy him a new sandwich,

230
00:14:42,340 --> 00:14:45,218
and past that, you're gonna ask
Mr. Williams for a broom

231
00:14:45,302 --> 00:14:46,636
to clean that up, you understand?

232
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:50,807
Right now, Damien, or you're mine
for another week of detention.

233
00:14:50,891 --> 00:14:52,251
I don't want to hear another word.

234
00:14:55,645 --> 00:14:57,230
It looks like you got the hang of it.

235
00:14:58,732 --> 00:15:00,108
What's up with you, duquan?

236
00:15:00,817 --> 00:15:01,943
Ain't nothing.

237
00:15:03,028 --> 00:15:04,362
You still at southwestern?

238
00:15:04,905 --> 00:15:08,283
Well, I'm, like, needing a semester off,
you know?

239
00:15:09,326 --> 00:15:10,452
I'm outdoors now.

240
00:15:13,205 --> 00:15:14,456
And...

241
00:15:14,748 --> 00:15:17,667
I was hoping maybe I could get with you

242
00:15:18,126 --> 00:15:21,505
and borrow some money,
so I can get a place and some clean clothes

243
00:15:21,588 --> 00:15:24,341
and get myself settled
so I can go back to school.

244
00:15:25,926 --> 00:15:27,010
