00:30:39,088 --> 00:30:40,339
Fran-zee kafka.

489
00:30:41,549 --> 00:30:42,675
Who's he?

490
00:30:43,259 --> 00:30:44,427
Some writer.

491
00:30:45,428 --> 00:30:46,762
You read his books?

492
00:30:47,346 --> 00:30:49,974
Fuck, no. But you remember flubber?

493
00:30:50,975 --> 00:30:55,646
He handed that to me the night that he had
me start leading the Saint Martin meeting.

494
00:30:57,273 --> 00:30:58,774
I kept it ever since.

495
00:31:00,776 --> 00:31:02,111
What it mean to you?

496
00:31:06,449 --> 00:31:07,950
You want these?

497
00:31:08,576 --> 00:31:11,370
Yeah, my man say he need it back
and not to make any copies.

498
00:31:13,456 --> 00:31:16,542
He say he ain't supposed to show it to me
before it goes in the paper.

499
00:31:16,959 --> 00:31:18,085
I mean, if! Let him.

500
00:31:18,669 --> 00:31:19,795
You gonna?

501
00:31:24,175 --> 00:31:25,384
Thanks for the crabs.

502
00:31:31,182 --> 00:31:32,641
Gray Van.

503
00:31:34,143 --> 00:31:35,311
You get the tag?

504
00:31:35,478 --> 00:31:36,878
I couldn't see it from where I was.

505
00:31:37,521 --> 00:31:38,856
Describe the driver.

506
00:31:39,273 --> 00:31:40,983
White. Six foot.

507
00:31:41,067 --> 00:31:43,903
Not heavy, not skinny either.

508
00:31:44,111 --> 00:31:45,321
Clothes?

509
00:31:45,738 --> 00:31:47,448
Nothing I noticed. Kinda nondescript.

510
00:31:48,032 --> 00:31:49,116
Nondescri pt?

511
00:31:49,992 --> 00:31:52,592
I was surprised, I guess. I just thought,
"whoa, what's he doing?"

512
00:31:53,496 --> 00:31:55,498
- Funny it being you to see this.
- It's weird.

513
00:31:55,664 --> 00:31:58,024
If an interview doesn't run late,
I'm not even here tonight.

514
00:31:59,627 --> 00:32:01,879
You mind if I get inside?
I gotta check in with my desk.

515
00:32:01,962 --> 00:32:03,602
You need anything else,
you got my number.

516
00:32:04,173 --> 00:32:05,257
Yeah.

517
00:32:10,930 --> 00:32:12,223
That guy's an asshole.

518
00:32:13,015 --> 00:32:14,575
This smokehound can't remember a thing.

519
00:32:15,434 --> 00:32:16,870
Only motherfucker
he remembers messing with him

520
00:32:16,894 --> 00:32:18,187
