521
00:32:18,354 --> 00:32:20,606
Whatever happened before that
is anyone's guess.

522
00:32:22,691 --> 00:32:23,692
Hey.

523
00:32:24,652 --> 00:32:27,863
Someone try to kidnap you,
drag you into a Van?

524
00:32:27,947 --> 00:32:29,073
Okay.

525
00:32:29,156 --> 00:32:30,699
