528
00:32:40,793 --> 00:32:42,044
What did you see, fella?

529
00:32:47,967 --> 00:32:48,968
Mcnulty?

530
00:32:51,303 --> 00:32:54,056
- Johnny Weaver. Tactical.
- Fuck you. Why didn't you say so?

531
00:32:54,140 --> 00:32:55,891
Jw. Tryin' to keep your cover?

532
00:32:55,975 --> 00:32:58,769
It's better if everyone here
thinks I'm one of the regulars, right?

533
00:32:59,436 --> 00:33:01,272
Anyway, what's the ruckus with petey?

534
00:33:01,355 --> 00:33:02,690
- The drunk?
- Yeah.

535
00:33:04,733 --> 00:33:06,652
Sun reporter says he's going
into his building,

536
00:33:06,735 --> 00:33:08,988
