into a gray Van.

537
00:33:09,738 --> 00:33:12,700
- It's bullshit, right?
- Yeah. Petey was laying there 45 minutes

538
00:33:12,783 --> 00:33:15,244
before that preppy cocksucker
even parks his car.

539
00:33:15,703 --> 00:33:17,163
- Thanks.
- No problem.

540
00:33:17,246 --> 00:33:19,081
Hey, gimme a dollar, make it look right.

541
00:33:23,002 --> 00:33:24,044
Thank you, Jimmy.

542
00:33:25,754 --> 00:33:29,091
What about the reporter? You could charge
