549
00:34:27,149 --> 00:34:29,336
Put 'em in the fridge.
Cold for lunch tomorrow, if you like.

550
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:30,444
I can't eat 'em all.

551
00:34:43,165 --> 00:34:45,251
We don't run this shit,
especially not off the front.

552
00:34:45,334 --> 00:34:49,797
- I saw what I saw.
- Alma is on the phone with police pio

553
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,924
and they are telling
us on the record and off

554
00:34:52,007 --> 00:34:54,969
that they are discounting any report
of a possible abduction.

555
00:34:55,094 --> 00:34:57,930
That doesn't mean they're doing their job,
and it doesn't mean we...

556
00:34:58,013 --> 00:35:01,267
Our job is to report the news,
not to manufacture it.

557
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:02,518
Fuck you, Gus.

558
00:35:04,353 --> 00:35:05,354
Nice.

559
00:35:12,945 --> 00:35:16,031
I know they're jealous of how much play
his stories get but the truth is...

560
00:35:16,115 --> 00:35:18,867
We cannot run this shit.

561
00:35:19,743 --> 00:35:21,703
Are you suggesting
that Scott made any of this up?

562
00:35:25,374 --> 00:35:27,918
You ever notice that the guys who do that,

563
00:35:28,544 --> 00:35:30,671
the blairs, the glasses, the kelleys,

564
