through the state desk.

579
00:36:11,962 --> 00:36:14,673
You should go home, think this through.

580
00:36:15,716 --> 00:36:16,759
We'll talk in the morning.

581
00:36:25,851 --> 00:36:27,978
Maybe you win a pulitzer with this stuff

582
00:36:29,063 --> 00:36:30,481
and maybe you gotta give it back.

583
00:36:32,983 --> 00:36:35,277
It's in my notes, Gus.
Everything that happened,

584
00:36:35,361 --> 00:36:37,446
everything that guy said when I got to him.

585
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:40,115
Every last word is in my notes.

586
00:37:02,471 --> 00:37:04,056
Home earlier than I thought.

587
00:37:04,807 --> 00:37:06,058
Yeah.

588
00:37:06,141 --> 00:37:07,142
Home.

589
00:37:22,324 --> 00:37:23,992
- He hit again.
- Who did?

590
00:37:24,076 --> 00:37:25,452
The serial killer.

591
00:37:26,495 --> 00:37:27,704
Get a grip, motherfucker.

592
00:37:27,788 --> 00:37:30,499
You don't believe me?
Check out his left wrist.

593
00:37:37,506 --> 00:37:39,174
You fuckin' with me again, bunk?

594
00:37:40,717 --> 00:37:42,010
Copycat.

595
00:37:43,303 --> 00:37:45,180
Call mcnulty. Get him down here.

596
00:37:52,229 --> 00:37:54,314
- Ronnie.
- Maury.

597
00:37:54,982 --> 00:37:58,652
Been going over the charging documents
on the partlow-Stanfield drug arrests.

598
00:37:58,777 --> 00:38:01,488
