No one's that brilliant,

602
00:38:08,829 --> 00:38:11,457
not at the bpd, anyway.

603
00:38:11,999 --> 00:38:13,584
You don't know Lester freamon.

604
00:38:13,667 --> 00:38:14,793
I know what I know.

605
00:38:15,794 --> 00:38:18,589
