613
00:38:40,569 --> 00:38:42,237
Whatever else you're running is illegal.

614
00:38:43,739 --> 00:38:44,907
Sources?

615
00:38:45,324 --> 00:38:47,951
Title threes are supposed
to be secret, Maury.

616
00:38:48,744 --> 00:38:51,914
Are you saying you have a source
of information inside the courthouse?

617
00:38:52,581 --> 00:38:54,291
- It's a figure of speech.
- Ah.

618
00:38:54,750 --> 00:38:57,961
What I'm saying is that
there's shit in the blood of your case,

619
00:38:58,086 --> 00:39:00,672
and, if you wait until this
goes past indictments,

620
00:39:01,298 --> 00:39:02,424
I'm gonna run wild with it.

621
00:39:04,259 --> 00:39:05,302
We should talk.

622
00:39:05,928 --> 00:39:07,137
Out of court.

623
00:39:11,141 --> 00:39:12,226
Fuck me.

624
00:39:14,603 --> 00:39:16,980
Is it enough?
Do you have enough?

625
00:39:17,064 --> 00:39:19,566
It has to be. It should be.

626
00:39:19,942 --> 00:39:22,027
You can't look at everything
that Robert found,

627
00:39:22,110 --> 00:39:24,655
at the pattern, and not see
what this fucking guy's about.

628
00:39:24,988 --> 00:39:26,990
You know that. I know that.

629
00:39:28,283 --> 00:39:29,409
What, you don't think so?

630
00:39:30,202 --> 00:39:31,745
I think that if you do this,

631
00:39:32,037 --> 00:39:33,789
these son of a bitches will do you.

632
00:39:35,541 --> 00:39:36,667
Come.

633
00:39:37,125 --> 00:39:39,419
Sorry. There's been
another homeless murder.

634
00:39:39,753 --> 00:39:40,963
South Baltimore.

635
00:39:43,757 --> 00:39:44,967
Careful, Gus.

636
00:39:45,676 --> 00:39:46,969
I can't protect you.

637
00:39:54,142 --> 00:39:55,519
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

638
00:39:58,313 --> 00:40:00,816
- No fucking way.
- Dead for a while.

639
00:40:01,149 --> 00:40:04,236
And I can assume, Jimmy,
from the fact that the ribbon ain't red

640
00:40:04,570 --> 00:40:07,698
and the fact that you don't need
another body because Mario is locked up...

641
00:40:07,781 --> 00:40:11,702
- I got nothing to do with this.
