642
00:40:12,661 --> 00:40:13,805
You see what you started here?

643
00:40:13,829 --> 00:40:16,498
The bosses are gonna toss it back to you.
No doubt.

644
00:40:16,582 --> 00:40:18,375
- The bosses know it's bullshit.
- What?

645
00:40:19,001 --> 00:40:21,420
- Daniels knows. Pearlman, too.
- How the fuck you...

646
00:40:25,215 --> 00:40:27,360
- How much longer does this...
- Can you give us a minute?

647
00:40:27,384 --> 00:40:30,262
You turning the world
upside down with your bullshit.

648
00:40:30,470 --> 00:40:32,431
- How are you not in jail?
- I don't know.

649
00:40:32,848 --> 00:40:34,683
The lie's so big,
people can't live with it.

650
00:40:34,766 --> 00:40:40,063
Jesus fucking Christ, Jimmy. I told you. I
fuckin' told you it was going to come to this.

651
00:40:40,939 --> 00:40:45,152
You played with fire, didn't you?
And now we're all getting burned...

652
00:40:46,403 --> 00:40:49,424
Reporting live from south
Baltimore, where police have found the body

653
00:40:49,448 --> 00:40:51,617
of what appears to be
another homeless man.

654
00:40:51,700 --> 00:40:54,077
This one killed and left in a vacant lot...

655
00:40:55,162 --> 00:40:57,456
Short while ago have refused so far...

656
00:40:57,831 --> 00:40:59,333
Did somebody not get the message?

657
00:41:38,205 --> 00:41:40,999
You're not killing them yourself, mcnulty,
at least assure me of that.

658
00:41:45,837 --> 00:41:47,214
And the one you disappeared?

659
00:41:48,757 --> 00:41:50,884
He's okay, last I checked.

660
00:41:51,009 --> 00:41:52,427
Good. That's a start...

661
00:41:54,012 --> 00:41:55,055
I guess.

662
00:41:55,138 --> 00:41:57,599
- I thought you got a message.
- Copycat.

663
00:41:59,476 --> 00:42:00,560
I got nothing on this one.

664
00:42:02,062 --> 00:42:03,146
Jesus.

665
00:42:03,230 --> 00:42:05,710
How did you do it? How did you get 'em
