666
00:42:06,775 --> 00:42:08,944
Some were real and I just linked 'em
with the ribbons.

667
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:11,697
Some ijuked as strangle jobs.

668
00:42:14,741 --> 00:42:17,369
- If it matters, I know now...
- Fuck what you know now.

669
00:42:17,953 --> 00:42:20,553
This was all for money, mcnulty?
You couldn't live without the ot?

670
00:42:22,040 --> 00:42:23,166
The Stanfield case.

671
00:42:23,792 --> 00:42:24,918
It was that.

672
00:42:25,043 --> 00:42:27,087
I know where it went,
but you got paid, too.

673
00:42:28,004 --> 00:42:30,465
You and freamon
and maybe a dozen other guys.

674
00:42:31,133 --> 00:42:32,384
It wasn't about the money.

675
00:42:42,018 --> 00:42:43,770
Down the road, when we settle on this,

676
00:42:43,979 --> 00:42:45,522
and we will settle on this,

677
00:42:46,648 --> 00:42:49,818
I don't expect any of you will ever see
another hour of ot again.

678
00:42:50,694 --> 00:42:53,488
I don't expect any of you
will be doing police work ever again.

679
00:42:54,156 --> 00:42:56,658
And the only reason
this isn't before a grand jury right now

680
00:42:56,950 --> 00:42:59,828
is because our mayor can't live with that.

681
00:43:00,620 --> 00:43:01,830
Oh, yeah.

682
00:43:02,038 --> 00:43:03,331
The mayor knows your name.

683
00:43:03,665 --> 00:43:05,751
So this is your last case.

684
00:43:06,585 --> 00:43:07,586
Work it.

685
00:43:07,669 --> 00:43:09,713
If you're half the
detective you think you are,

686
00:43:10,088 --> 00:43:12,841
you'll put this one down fast
and take us all off the hook.

687
00:43:13,341 --> 00:43:14,926
The longer this goes on,

688
00:43:15,594 --> 00:43:17,012
the worse the payback's gonna be.

689
00:43:35,822 --> 00:43:36,982
But what does he really know?

690
00:43:37,240 --> 00:43:40,869
What he knows now isn't half of what
he'll learn when we get to discovery.

691
00:43:41,203 --> 00:43:43,789
They won't be able to produce
a credible source of information.

692
00:43:43,872 --> 00:43:46,333
They don't have to if
it's not a registered ci

693
00:43:47,042 --> 00:43:48,084
a source is only...

694
00:43:48,168 --> 00:43:49,808
If he can raise doubts in a judge's mind,

695
00:43:49,878 --> 00:43:51,963
we could be compelled to reveal our source.

696
00:43:52,422 --> 00:43:54,466
At that point, we're giving up the wiretap.

697
00:43:54,633 --> 00:43:56,676
And he gets the papennork
from the phone company.

698
00:43:56,760 --> 00:43:58,386
Which has Stanfield's number on it.

699
00:43:59,471 --> 00:44:00,680
God.

700
00:44:02,432 --> 00:44:04,851
The only thing we can do is barter.

701
00:44:05,060 --> 00:44:06,686
Then barter. This can't go to court.

702
00:44:06,895 --> 00:44:08,104
We do have some leverage.

703
00:44:09,314 --> 00:44:10,398
What?

704
00:44:12,150 --> 00:44:15,946
Let's just say Mr. Levy has problems
