705
00:44:17,364 --> 00:44:18,740
Make this go away...

706
00:44:20,075 --> 00:44:22,452
And the mayor will not
forget that you did so.

707
00:44:23,829 --> 00:44:24,913
Nor will I.

708
00:44:27,916 --> 00:44:30,293
Jimmy, ass up an' help us with this.

709
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:33,088
Shit is funky.

710
00:44:38,593 --> 00:44:42,514
- We should take this into the box.
