711
00:44:42,597 --> 00:44:44,997
We have questions
about the reported kidnapping...

712
00:44:46,685 --> 00:44:48,565
- Those two bags there.
- Yes, ma'am.

713
00:44:50,021 --> 00:44:52,501
Well, that would seem
to be the newspaper's problem.

714
00:44:54,109 --> 00:44:56,236
I get another fucking
call about a gray Van,

715
00:44:56,319 --> 00:44:58,947
I'm burning that fucking newspaper building
